ModelRequest(parts=[UserPromptPart(content='Question: For each air handling unit whose label contains rtu, identify any connectable element it contains that observes or has property a property, or any property it has directly, and for each property give its label along with the ALC endpoint and the MPC database name from its external reference', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 19, 7, 35, 0, 200471, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), part_kind='user-prompt')], instructions=None, kind='request')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{"sparql_query": "PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.3/Brick#>\\nPREFIX bf: <https://example.org/buildingfacade#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?ahu ?ahuLabel ?property ?propertyLabel ?endpoint ?dbName WHERE {\\n  # Air handling units whose label contains \\"rtu\\"\\n  ?ahu a brick:Air_Handling_Unit ;\\n       rdfs:label ?ahuLabel .\\n  FILTER regex(?ahuLabel, \\"rtu\\", \\"i\\")\\n\\n  # Either a property directly attached to the AHU\\n  { \\n    ?ahu bf:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n  UNION\\n  # Or a property attached to a connectable element contained in the AHU\\n  {\\n    ?ahu bf:hasPart ?elem .\\n    ?elem a bf:ConnectableElement .\\n    { ?elem bf:observes ?property } UNION { ?elem bf:hasProperty ?property }\\n  }\\n\\n  # Pull the property label\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?propertyLabel .\\n\\n  # External reference \\u2013 endpoint (ALC) and MPC database name, if present\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?property bf:hasExternalReference ?ref .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?ref bf:hasEndpoint ?endpoint . }\\n    OPTIONAL { ?ref bf:hasDatabaseName ?dbName . }\\n  }\\n}\\n"}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-745dde3b19194339a8e7357df78e5196', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 19, 7, 35, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
